io.vertx.sqlclient.data

Class NullValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.vertx.sqlclient.data.NullValue

  • public class NullValue
extends Object
    Instances of this class indicate the type associated with a NULL column value. This is useful when infering database types from Tuple items.
